prodNameC: 迪爾埃氧化劑偵測試劑
ingredientsDesc:
General Oxidant-Detect Reagent: Contains 2×500 mL of 3,31,5,51 tetramethylbenzidine in an acidic solution.
General Oxidant-Detect Calibrator Kit: Contains 1×25 mL of negative calibrator and 1×25 mL of 200μg/mL nitrite in an aqueous solution.
General Oxidant-Detect Control Kit: Contains 1×25 mL of Negative Control (100μg/mL nitrite) and 1×25 mL of Positive Control (300 μg/mL nitrite) in an aqueous solution.
